item.title: CVE-2023-5955|2024-10-01T14:35:50.973Z -- unknown -- contact%20form%20email
item.description: The Contact Form Email WordPress plugin before 1.3.44 does not sanitise and escape some of its settings, which could allow high privilege users such as admin to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed (for example in multisite setup)
